=Description=

"Rafi Haladjian invented the Nabaztag, the connected rabbit that invaded thousands of houses in the past years. He is now taking on a much bigger challenge: connecting all of our daily objects. In this talk, he brings a down-to-earth approach to the Internet of Things with a raw unglamourized vision of what this technology enables."


